During a road trip I wanted to stop by the VW Thing Mecca.
Very friendly team.
A little disappointed they didn't have some parts I needed.
Just a reminder that some of our Thing parts are hard to come by.

A fun stop on a long road.

An incredible place with high quality aftermarket and original parts.
They actually manufacture some of the parts themselves in an effort to keep our Things on the road.
Incredible place, friendly helpful staff and reasonable prices.

